<h2 id="introduction">Introduction.</h2>
<p>This is the part two of android pentest, part one documentation is found <a href="https://gemstone-source.github.io/android-pentest/">here</a>. 
On this documentation I will show how to intercept android application traffics with using <code class="language-plaintext highlighter-rouge">burpsuite</code>.  In previous post I showed how to capture traffics from google web apps but using same methodology on intercepting <code class="language-plaintext highlighter-rouge">android apk</code> wont work.  To do this some steps will be followed as explained below:-</p>
